OL,3,CSunday school teacher killed in Omagh
OL,4,Cbomb lived life of 'kindness and love'
OL,6,FA Sunday school teacher's murder in
OL,7,Fthe Omagh bomb cut short a life rich
OL,8,Fin kindness, love and promise, the
OL,9,Finquiry into the outrage has heard.
OL,11,FEsther Gibson, 36, was engaged to be
OL,12,Fmarried at the time of her death in
OL,13,FAugust 1998 when a dissident
OL,14,Frepublican car bomb exploded in the
OL,15,Fcentre of the Co Tyrone market town on
OL,16,Fa busy Saturday afternoon.
OL,18,FThe trained secretary, who worked at
OL,19,Fan Omagh clothing manufacturing
OL,20,Ffactory, was one of 29 people who lost
OL,21,Ftheir lives on the day.
