OL,6,FThe second week of commemorative
OL,7,Fhearings for the victims began with a
OL,8,Ftribute written by Ms Gibson's four
OL,9,Fyounger sisters.
OL,11,FIt was read by one of her nieces in a
OL,12,Frecorded presentation played to
OL,13,Finquiry chairman Lord Turnbull.
OL,15,FIt described how Ms Gibson had grown
OL,16,Fup as part of a tight knit family that
OL,17,Flived on a farm near Beragh, Co Tyrone.
