OL,6,FIn that environment she developed a
OL,7,F"strong sense of duty and compassion
OL,8,Fthat would characterise her life", the
OL,9,Fstatement said.
OL,11,FMs Gibson's sisters spoke of the "joy
OL,12,Fand purpose" she found in her strong
OL,13,FChristian faith. She was a regular
OL,14,Fattender at Sixmilecross Free
OL,15,FPresbyterian Church, where she was
OL,16,Fknown for her "warmth and generosity".
