OL,6,F"Esther was also actively involved in
OL,7,Fher church community, teaching Sunday
OL,8,Fschool classes and serving as a role
OL,9,Fmodel for the younger generation," the
OL,10,Fsisters' statement said.
OL,12,F"Her commitment to her faith and to
OL,13,Fhelping others was evident in all
OL,14,Faspects of her life.
