OL,6,F"At the time of her death, Esther was
OL,7,Fengaged to be married, looking forward
OL,8,Fto a future filled with hope and
OL,9,Fhappiness. She was a young woman with
OL,10,Fmuch to look forward to. Her career
OL,11,Fwas flourishing, her faith was strong,
OL,12,Fand she was preparing to embark on a
OL,13,Fnew chapter of her life with her
OL,14,Ffiance.
OL,16,F"Esther's murder cut short a life that
OL,17,Fwas rich in kindness, love and promise.
OL,26,@nD@AOUxD@AOU
