OL,6,F"She was deeply loved by her family,
OL,7,Ffriends and community, and her absence
OL,8,Fis profoundly felt by all who knew
OL,9,Fher."
OL,11,FOne of Ms Gibson's sisters ` Caroline
OL,12,FMartin ` then read a poem to the
OL,13,Finquiry that was written by a close
OL,14,Frelative in the months after her death.
OL,16,FThe poem was about her absence from Ms
OL,17,FMartin's wedding, which took place
OL,18,Faround six weeks after the bombing.
